[11.245348, "i", "ls -la /app/docs && sed -n '1,200p' /app/docs/layout.md\n"]
[11.245851, "o", "ls -la /app/docs && sed -n '1,200p' /app/docs/layout.md\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[11.249138, "o", "total 8\r\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root   44 May 28 23:38 .\r\ndrwxr-xr-x 20 root root  264 May 28 23:39 ..\r\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 1344 May 28 23:38 layout.md\r\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root  681 May 28 23:38 operations.md\r\n# Audit output layout\r\n\r\n`/app/output/conservation_audit.json` holds a single object with a `cases`\r\narray. The per-case helpers emit the same object shape with one entry.\r\n\r\nEach entry has these fields:\r\n\r\n- `name` — scenario identifier.\r\n- `base_total` — three running sums of the starting state, one per tracked\r\n  quantity.\r\n- `after_total` — the same three sums measured once the structural phases of\r\n  the run have completed.\r\n- `resumed_total` — a position-weighted moment of the final state (each cell's\r\n  contribution scaled by its ordinal position). Two runs of the same scenario\r\n  that reach the same end arrangement report the same moment.\r\n- `drift_ratio` — the largest relative gap between `after_total` and\r\n  `base_total` across the three quantities.\r\n- `balanced` — true when the seam accounting over every coarse-fine interface\r\n  closed out.\r\n- `base_match` — true when `after_total` matches `base_total` within the\r\n  numerical floor.\r\n- `adjacency` — count of parent/child links resolved at the structural peak of\r\n  the run.\r\n- `halo_q` — three sampled ghost-band values taken at the first refined seam.\r\n\r\n`/app/output/persistence_audit.log` records one line per snapshot load attempt\r\nduring the runs that round-trip through `/app/work/vault.bin`. A line begins\r\nwith `ACCEPTED` or `REJECTED`; rejected lines name the reason.\r\n"]
[11.250282, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@a48c1a67d572:/app# "]
[11.382169, "i", "sed -n '1,240p' /app/docs/operations.md\n"]
[11.382611, "o", "sed -n '1,240p' /app/docs/operations.md\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[11.385327, "o", "# Operations\r\n\r\nBuild the driver with CMake:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncmake -S /app -B /app/build\r\ncmake --build /app/build -j2\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe driver lands at `/app/build/bin/sim_run`. The wrappers under\r\n`/app/scripts` invoke it:\r\n"]
[11.385583, "o", "\r\n- `bash /app/scripts/run-matrix.sh` runs every bundled scenario and writes\r\n  `/app/output/conservation_audit.json`.\r\n- `bash /app/scripts/run-one.sh <name>` writes `/app/output/<name>-audit.json`.\r\n- `bash /app/scripts/run-replay.sh <name>` writes\r\n  `/app/output/<name>-replay.json`.\r\n\r\nScenario schedules live in `/app/config/cases.toml`. Starting states live in\r\n`/app/data/init`. Snapshots are written under `/app/work` during scenarios\r\nthat round-trip through a saved checkpoint.\r\n"]
[11.385711, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@a48c1a67d572:/app# "]
[11.502655, "i", "sed -n '1,240p' /app/config/cases.toml\n"]
[11.503172, "o", "sed -n '1,240p' /app/config/cases.toml"]
[11.503613, "o", "\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[11.504987, "o", "# Per-scenario schedules for the bundled sweep.\r\n# profile selects the initial-condition table under /app/data/init.\r\n# leaves is a '|'-separated list (one entry per base cell); each entry is a\r\n# comma-separated list of integer sub-cell weights for that base cell.\r\n# do_flux / do_collapse / do_restart toggle the structural phases.\r\n\r\n"]
[11.505439, "o", "[storm]\r\nprofile = 0\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 1\r\ndo_collapse = 0\r\ndo_restart = 0\r\nleaves = 2,1,1|1|1|1\r\n\r\n[canyon]\r\nprofile = 1\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 1\r\ndo_collapse = 0\r\ndo_restart = 0\r\nleaves = 2,1,1|2,2|1|1\r\n\r\n"]
[11.505555, "o", "[plume]\r\nprofile = 2\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 0\r\ndo_collapse = 1\r\ndo_restart = 0\r\nleaves = 2,1|3,1|1|1\r\n\r\n[spire]\r\nprofile = 0\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 0\r\ndo_collapse = 1\r\ndo_restart = 0\r\nleaves = 3,1|1|1|1\r\n\r\n[basin]\r\nprofile = 1\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 1\r\ndo_collapse = 0\r\ndo_restart = 1\r\nleaves = 2,1,1|1|1|1\r\n\r\n[dune]\r\nprofile = 2\r\nn_coarse = 4\r\ndo_flux = 1\r\ndo_collapse = 0\r\ndo_restart = 1\r\nleaves = 2,1,1|2,2|1|1\r\n\u001b[?2004hroot@a48c1a67d572:/app# "]
